    "description": "Noodle Samurai is a top down action game about Reshi, a samurai monkey, turned chef. Reshi is forced to hack 'n' slash his way through a series of sentient ingredients and deliver them to the demon toad before he loses his patience and eats Reshi instead. In order to deliver the ingredients as fast as possible Reshi must use his wits and grappling hook to traverse the various arenas across the land.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore over 90 action packed levels.<br></li><li>Outplay your enemies with Reshi's dash and parry abilities.<br></li><li>Race against the clock to earn yourself a bronze, silver or gold medal.<br></li><li>Complete each level faster than your friends to secure your place at the top of the leaderboard.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grapple Across Arenas!</h2>Traverse the map with your grappling hook.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153240/extras/041fbe9d32a4e9332832d964da7c279f.poster.avif?t=1755151727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153240/extras/041fbe9d32a4e9332832d964da7c279f.webm?t=1755151727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153240/extras/041fbe9d32a4e9332832d964da7c279f.mp4?t=1755151727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Ingredients!</h2>Battle the ingredients to collect them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153240/extras/04be465dc6c7902cc1d96328c3e33778.poster.avif?t=1755151727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153240/extras/04be465dc6c7902cc1d96328c3e33778.webm?t=1755151727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs